desc: NAHEYIYI Contemporary Art Designed Studio located in Toronto Canada. Each piece is created by hand, combined with 3D CAD technology. These ideas are inspired by nature and comes from social and global issues. Working mainly in silver, copper, nature gem (labradorite, maligano etc. ) and resin.

layout.text: It's a story of evolution. We are new creatures named Morphi. We are adapting the new world and learning from it.
